{"tid":1864674,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 武漢肺炎爆發期間仲應唔應該遊行集會？","createTime":"2020-02-05T17:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T02:37:28.000Z","uid":27626,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"361aaed56131528dc62daef970470678b7e0da1b","tid":1864674,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:30:52.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】聚會變播毒！中國多宗集體感染個案 寧波祈福25人中招<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1861869\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1861869</a><br />\n睇完呢個呢post喺度諗<br />\n武漢肺炎喺香港社區爆發的話<br />\n咁仲應唔應該繼續有遊行集會？<br />\n如果停咗又比人話運動已完<br />\n出黎既話成本效益好低，都係為咗畫面好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又要冒住有集體感染既風險仲未必有口罩出到黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好撚驚一個唔好彩手足一齊攬炒做肺炎師<br />\n大家一齊研究下抗疫期間如何繼續抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續抗爭遊行集會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷工自我隔離啦屌"},{"pid":"9ad5329254497f72d9ec9c5fd70a878b3e4198be","tid":1864674,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:31:33.000Z","msg":"全力支持醫護罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90033f1f8c3a4db1a070c6145ba7cb02e94ed10","tid":1864674,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:32:27.000Z","msg":"祝各位手足身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aac6be9f6d3171ab1a44f9773607adc287cd1c9","tid":1864674,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:32:46.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"2e4293277170fbdf3c37333ea84346006de52e02","tid":1864674,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T17:33:04.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"e260405856619f1a1c8b0d3b7df093b2d0e25bc8","tid":1864674,"uid":27626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit